HEADWORD: Infestation
<hw>In`fes*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>infestatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>infestation</ets>.]</ety> <def>The
